  "math_track": ["5pt"],
  "title_en": "Dot Product, Projection & Cross Product in 3D",
  "title_he": "מכפלה סקalarית, הטלה ומכפלה וקטורית ב-3D",
  "summary_en": "Dot product, vector projection, cross product, and triangle area in 3D.",
  "summary_he": "מכפלה סקalarית, הטלה, מכפלה וקטורית ושטח משולש ב-3D.",
  "est_minutes": 40,
  "sections": [
    {"kind":"intro","title_en":"3D Vectors — Dot and Cross","title_he":"וקטורים ב-3D","body_en_md":"In 3D, the **dot product** measures alignment (scalar), while the **cross product** produces a vector perpendicular to both inputs — essential for area and torque.\n\nBagrut 5-unit geometry uses $\\vec{u}=(u_1,u_2,u_3)$ component-wise.","body_he_md":"**מכפלה סקalarית** מודדת יישור; **מכפלה וקטורית** יוצרת וקטור מאונך — חיוני לשטח.\n\nב-5 יחידות: $\\vec{u}=(u_1,u_2,u_3)$."},
    {"kind":"definition","title_en":"Key Formulas","title_he":"נוסחאות מרכזיות","body_en_md":"$$\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=u_1v_1+u_2v_2+u_3v_3=|\\vec{u}||\\vec{v}|\\cos\\theta$$\n$$\\text{proj}_{\\vec{u}}\\vec{v}=\\frac{\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}}{|\\vec{u}|^2}\\vec{u}$$\n$$\\vec{u}\\times\\vec{v}=\\begin{vmatrix}\\hat{i}&\\hat{j}&\\hat{k}\\\\u_1&u_2&u_3\\\\v_1&v_2&v_3\\end{vmatrix},\\quad |\\vec{u}\\times\\vec{v}|=|\\vec{u}||\\vec{v}|\\sin\\theta$$\n$$\\text{Triangle area}=\\frac{1}{2}|\\vec{AB}\\times\\vec{AC}|$$","body_he_md":"$$\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=u_1v_1+u_2v_2+u_3v_3$$\n$$\\text{proj}_{\\vec{u}}\\vec{v}=\\frac{\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}}{|\\vec{u}|^2}\\vec{u}$$\n$$|\\vec{u}\\times\\vec{v}|=|\\vec{u}||\\vec{v}|\\sin\\theta,\\quad \\text{שטח}=\\frac{1}{2}|\\vec{AB}\\times\\vec{AC}|$$"},
    {"kind":"theory","title_en":"Dot, Projection, Cross","title_he":"תיאוריה","body_en_md":"**Orthogonal:** $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=0$.\n\n**Cross product:** anti-commutative ($\\vec{u}\\times\\vec{v}=-\\vec{v}\\times\\vec{u}$), zero when parallel.\n\n**Right-hand rule** gives direction of $\\vec{u}\\times\\vec{v}$.","body_he_md":"**ניצבות:** $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=0$.\n\n**מכפלה וקטורית:** אנטי-קומutative; אפס כשמקבילים.\n\n**כלל יד ימין** לכיוון."},
    {"kind":"worked_example","difficulty":"easy","example_number":1,"title_en":"Worked Example 1 — Dot Product and Angle","title_he":"דוגמה 1 — מכפלה סקalarית וזווית","body_en_md":"**Given:** $\\vec{u}=(2,1,-1)$, $\\vec{v}=(3,0,2)$.\n\n**Step 1:** Dot: $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=2(3)+1(0)+(-1)(2)=6-2=4$.\n\n**Step 2:** $|\\vec{u}|=\\sqrt{4+1+1}=\\sqrt{6}$, $|\\vec{v}|=\\sqrt{9+4}=\\sqrt{13}$.\n\n**Step 3:** $\\cos\\theta=\\frac{4}{\\sqrt{78}}$.\n\n**Step 4:** $\\theta=\\arccos(4/\\sqrt{78})\\approx27.2°$.\n\n**Answer:** $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=4$, $\\theta\\approx27°$.","body_he_md":"**נתון:** $\\vec{u}=(2,1,-1)$, $\\vec{v}=(3,0,2)$.\n\n**שלב 1:** $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=4$.\n\n**שלב 2:** $|\\vec{u}|=\\sqrt{6}$, $|\\vec{v}|=\\sqrt{13}$.\n\n**שלב 3:** $\\cos\\theta=4/\\sqrt{78}$.\n\n**שלב 4:** $\\theta\\approx27°$."},
    {"kind":"checkpoint","title_en":"Stop & Practice","title_he":"עצור ותרגל","body_en_md":"$\\vec{a}=(1,0,0)$, $\\vec{b}=(0,1,0)$. Find $\\vec{a}\\cdot\\vec{b}$.","body_he_md":"$\\vec{a}=(1,0,0)$, $\\vec{b}=(0,1,0)$. מצא $\\vec{a}\\cdot\\vec{b}$.","checkpoint_solution_en":"$\\vec{a}\\cdot\\vec{b}=0$ (perpendicular).","checkpoint_solution_he":"$\\vec{a}\\cdot\\vec{b}=0$ (ניצבים)."},
    {"kind":"worked_example","difficulty":"medium","example_number":2,"title_en":"Worked Example 2 — Projection of v onto u","title_he":"דוגמה 2 — הטלת v על u","body_en_md":"**Given:** $\\vec{u}=(2,1,-1)$, $\\vec{v}=(3,0,2)$; $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=4$, $|\\vec{u}|^2=6$.\n\n**Step 1:** $\\text{proj}_{\\vec{u}}\\vec{v}=\\frac{4}{6}\\vec{u}=\\frac{2}{3}(2,1,-1)$.\n\n**Step 2:** $=\\left(\\frac{4}{3},\\frac{2}{3},-\\frac{2}{3}\\right)$.\n\n**Step 3:** Check: projection parallel to $\\vec{u}$ ✓.\n\n**Answer:** $\\text{proj}_{\\vec{u}}\\vec{v}=\\left(\\frac{4}{3},\\frac{2}{3},-\\frac{2}{3}\\right)$.","body_he_md":"**נתון:** $\\vec{u}=(2,1,-1)$, $\\vec{v}=(3,0,2)$.\n\n**שלב 1:** $\\text{proj}=\\frac{4}{6}\\vec{u}$.\n\n**שלב 2:** $\\left(\\frac{4}{3},\\frac{2}{3},-\\frac{2}{3}\\right)$.\n\n**תשובה:** $\\left(\\frac{4}{3},\\frac{2}{3},-\\frac{2}{3}\\right)$."},
    {"kind":"checkpoint","title_en":"Stop & Practice","title_he":"עצור ותרגל","body_en_md":"Are $\\vec{u}$ and $\\vec{v}$ from Example 1 perpendicular?","body_he_md":"האם $\\vec{u}$ ו-$\\vec{v}$ מדוגמה 1 ניצבים?","checkpoint_solution_en":"No — dot product is 4 ≠ 0.","checkpoint_solution_he":"לא — המכפלה 4 ≠ 0."},
    {"kind":"worked_example","difficulty":"hard","example_number":3,"title_en":"Worked Example 3 — Triangle Area via Cross Product","title_he":"דוגמה 3 — שטח משולש","body_en_md":"**Given:** Triangle with $A(0,0,0)$, $B(2,0,0)$, $C(0,3,1)$.\n\n**Step 1:** $\\vec{AB}=(2,0,0)$, $\\vec{AC}=(0,3,1)$.\n\n**Step 2:** $\\vec{AB}\\times\\vec{AC}=(0,-2,6)$.\n\n**Step 3:** $|\\vec{AB}\\times\\vec{AC}|=\\sqrt{40}=2\\sqrt{10}$.\n\n**Step 4:** Area $=\\frac{1}{2}(2\\sqrt{10})=\\sqrt{10}$.\n\n**Answer:** Area $=\\sqrt{10}$ square units.","body_he_md":"**נתון:** $A(0,0,0)$, $B(2,0,0)$, $C(0,3,1)$.\n\n**שלב 1:** $\\vec{AB}=(2,0,0)$, $\\vec{AC}=(0,3,1)$.\n\n**שלב 2:** $\\vec{AB}\\times\\vec{AC}=(0,-2,6)$.\n\n**שלב 3–4:** שטח $=\\sqrt{10}$."},
    {"kind":"method_guide","title_en":"Method Guide","title_he":"מדריך שיטה","body_en_md":"| Task | Method |\n|---|---|\n| Angle | $\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}}{|\\vec{u}||\\vec{v}|}$ |\n| Projection | $\\frac{\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}}{|\\vec{u}|^2}\\vec{u}$ |\n| Perpendicular | Dot = 0 |\n| Triangle area | $\\frac{1}{2}|\\vec{AB}\\times\\vec{AC}|$ |","body_he_md":"| משימה | שיטה |\n|---|---|\n| זווית | dot |\n| הטלה | $\\frac{\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}}{|\\vec{u}|^2}\\vec{u}$ |\n| ניצבות | dot=0 |\n| שטח | $\\frac{1}{2}|\\times|$ |"},
