      {"id":"vdh3","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Vector ⊥ to $(1,0,1)$ and $(0,1,1)$.","body_he":"וקטור ⟂ ל-$(1,0,1)$ ו-$(0,1,1)$.","solution_en":"$(-1,-1,1)$","solution_he":"$(-1,-1,1)$"},
      {"id":"vdh4","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Prove $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=0$ iff orthogonal.","body_he":"הוכח: $\\vec{u}\\cdot\\vec{v}=0$ ⟺ ניצבים.","solution_en":"$\\cos90°=0$ ⟺ dot=0","solution_he":"$\\cos90°=0$ ⟺ dot=0"}
    ]},
    {"kind":"pitfall","title_en":"Common Pitfalls","title_he":"מלכודות נפוצות","body_en_md":"1. **Using $|u||v|$ instead of $|u|^2$** in projection.\n2. **Cross order matters**.\n3. **Forgetting $\\frac{1}{2}$** for triangle area.\n4. **Sign errors in cross determinant**.","body_he_md":"1. **$|u|^2$ בהטלה**.\n2. **סדר cross**.\n3. **$\\frac{1}{2}$ בשטח**.\n4. **סימן בדטרמיננטה**."},
    {"kind":"before_exam","title_en":"Before the Exam","title_he":"לפני הבחינה","body_en_md":"- Dot = sum of products; cross = determinant.\n- proj uses $|u|^2$.\n- Area = half |cross|.\n- Orthogonal ⟺ dot = 0.","body_he_md":"- Dot; cross; הטלה; שטח; ניצבות."},
    {"kind":"summary","title_en":"Take-away","title_he":"סיכום","body_en_md":"- Dot → angle and projection.\n- Cross → area.\n- Work component-wise in 3D.","body_he_md":"- Dot → זווית והטלה.\n- Cross → שטח.\n- רכיבים ב-3D."}
